column4: Tesla plans to raise funds this year to tackle cash crunch
column5: Facing a severe cash crunch  Tesla Motors Inc plans to raise additional money this year to help fund development and production of its new Model 3 sedan and build out a massive battery factory  the company said on Wednesday.
